#. <section class="sutta" id="sn17.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn17.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The First Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 8. Siṅgālasutta → sigālasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn17.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Siṅgālasutta"
msgstr "8. A Jackal"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.231"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn17.8:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn17.8:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … adhigamāya."
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal …"

#. VAR: jarasiṅgālassa → jarasigālassa (bj, s1-3, km) | siṅgālassa (pts1-2, mr)
msgctxt "sn17.8:1.3"
msgid ""
"Assuttha no tumhe, bhikkhave, rattiyā paccūsasamayaṃ jarasiṅgālassa "
"vassamānassā”ti?"
msgstr "Mendicants, did you hear an old jackal howling at the crack of dawn?”"

msgctxt "sn17.8:1.4"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

#. VAR: ukkaṇḍakena → ukkaṇṭakena (bj) | ukkannakena (si) | ukkaṇṇakena (s1-3, km, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn17.8:1.5"
msgid ""
"“Eso kho, bhikkhave, jarasiṅgālo ukkaṇḍakena nāma rogajātena phuṭṭho neva "
"bilagato ramati, na rukkhamūlagato ramati, na ajjhokāsagato ramati;"
msgstr ""
"“That old jackal has the disease called mange. He’s not happy in his den, or "
"at the root of a tree, or out in the open."

msgctxt "sn17.8:1.6"
msgid ""
"yena yena gacchati, yattha yattha tiṭṭhati, yattha yattha nisīdati, yattha "
"yattha nipajjati; tattha tattha anayabyasanaṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"Wherever he goes, stands, sits, or lies down he meets with tragedy and "
"disaster."

msgctxt "sn17.8:1.7"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhikkhu lābhasakkārasilokena abhibhūto "
"pariyādiṇṇacitto neva suññāgāragato ramati, na rukkhamūlagato ramati, na "
"ajjhokāsagato ramati;"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, take a certain mendicant whose mind is overcome and "
"overwhelmed by possessions, honor, and popularity. They’re not happy in an "
"empty hut, at the root of a tree, or out in the open."

msgctxt "sn17.8:1.8"
msgid ""
"yena yena gacchati, yattha yattha tiṭṭhati, yattha yattha nisīdati, yattha "
"yattha nipajjati; tattha tattha anayabyasanaṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"Wherever they go, stand, sit, or lie down they meet with tragedy and "
"disaster."

msgctxt "sn17.8:1.9"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …”"

msgctxt "sn17.8:1.10"
msgid "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.8:1.11"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
